BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 720.00 Td (Quartus builds/configures FPGA hardware. OpenVINO plus the FPGA AI Suite runtime runs inference.) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 707.50 Td (Quartus does not replace OpenVINO runtime.) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 18 Tf 0.050 0.180 0.350 rg 54.00 669.00 Td (Part A - Windows 11 installation flow) Tj ET
