BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 499.38 Td (2. Install it with WSL 2 backend enabled if prompted.) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 482.88 Td (3. Restart Windows.) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 466.38 Td (4. Open PowerShell and test:) Tj ET
