BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 360.62 Td (docker pull alterafpga/fpgaaisuite:2026.1.1-quartus) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 340.00 Td (For smaller compiler/emulation-only use:) Tj ET
