BT /Helvetica 8 Tf 0.350 0.350 0.350 rg 54.00 738.00 Td (FPGA AI Suite 2026.1.1 Installation Guide) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 720.00 Td (You are inside FPGA AI Suite when the prompt changes from a Windows prompt like:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 697.50 Td (PS C:\\Users\\name>) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 676.88 Td (to a Linux container prompt like:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 654.38 Td (fpga_ai_suite@container_id:~$) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 633.75 Td (Then go to your workspace and reload the local FPGA AI Suite work environment:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 611.25 Td (cd /workspace/quickstart) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 600.62 Td (source ./coredla_work.sh) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 580.00 Td (If the workspace has not been created yet, use the workspace setup section later in this guide.) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 559.50 Td (To exit the container:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 537.00 Td (exit) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 516.38 Td (Do not create a new container every day unless you intentionally want a clean environment. Use) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 503.88 Td (docker start -ai for daily work.) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 14 Tf 0.050 0.250 0.450 rg 54.00 479.38 Td (A7. Verify inside Docker) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 453.88 Td (Prompt should look like:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 431.38 Td (fpga_ai_suite@container_id:~$) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 410.75 Td (Run:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 388.25 Td (python3 -c "import openvino; print\(openvino.__version__\)") Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 377.62 Td (echo $COREDLA_ROOT) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 367.00 Td (dla_compiler --version) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 356.38 Td (quartus_pgm --version) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 345.75 Td (jtagconfig) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 325.12 Td (Expected OpenVINO version begins with:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 302.62 Td (2025.4) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 282.00 Td (If no FPGA board is connected, jtagconfig may show:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 259.50 Td (No JTAG hardware available) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 238.88 Td (That is normal.) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 18 Tf 0.050 0.180 0.350 rg 54.00 200.38 Td (Part B - Linux/Ubuntu Docker installation flow) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 14 Tf 0.050 0.250 0.450 rg 54.00 165.88 Td (B1. Recommended for Ubuntu 26.04) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 140.38 Td (Ubuntu 26.04 is not officially listed as a native FPGA AI Suite target. Use Docker.) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 14 Tf 0.050 0.250 0.450 rg 54.00 115.88 Td (B2. Install Docker Engine) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 88.38 Td (sudo apt update) Tj ET
