BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 67.12 Td (sudo install -m 0755 -d /etc/apt/keyrings) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 8 Tf 0.4 0.4 0.4 rg 286.00 28 Td (Page 3 of 13) Tj ET
endstream
