BT /Helvetica 8 Tf 0.350 0.350 0.350 rg 54.00 738.00 Td (FPGA AI Suite 2026.1.1 Installation Guide) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 720.00 Td (curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 709.38 Td (  o /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 698.75 Td (sudo chmod a+r /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 678.12 Td (If Docker has a repo for your Ubuntu codename, use it. If not, use the Ubuntu 24.04 noble repo:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 655.62 Td (echo "deb [arch=$\(dpkg --print-architecture\) signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/docke) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 645.00 Td (  r.gpg] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu noble stable" | sudo tee /etc/) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 634.38 Td (  apt/sources.list.d/docker.list > /dev/null) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 613.75 Td (Install Docker:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 591.25 Td (sudo apt update) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 580.62 Td (sudo apt install -y docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io docker-buildx-plugin) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 570.00 Td (   docker-compose-plugin) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 559.38 Td (sudo systemctl enable docker) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 548.75 Td (sudo systemctl start docker) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 538.12 Td (sudo usermod -aG docker $USER) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 517.50 Td (Log out and log back in. Test:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 495.00 Td (docker run hello-world) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 14 Tf 0.050 0.250 0.450 rg 54.00 470.38 Td (B3. Pull complete FPGA AI Suite image) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 442.88 Td (docker pull alterafpga/fpgaaisuite:2026.1.1-quartus) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 14 Tf 0.050 0.250 0.450 rg 54.00 418.25 Td (B4. Create workspace) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 390.75 Td (mkdir -p ~/fpga-ai-work) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 14 Tf 0.050 0.250 0.450 rg 54.00 366.12 Td (B5. Run container with USB/JTAG support) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 340.62 Td (Use this command if you may connect an FPGA board later:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 318.12 Td (docker run -it \\) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 307.50 Td (  --name fpga-ai-suite-2026 \\) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 296.88 Td (  --privileged \\) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 286.25 Td (  -v /dev/bus/usb:/dev/bus/usb \\) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 275.62 Td (  -v ~/fpga-ai-work:/workspace \\) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 265.00 Td (  alterafpga/fpgaaisuite:2026.1.1-quartus) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 244.38 Td (Restart later:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 221.88 Td (docker start -ai fpga-ai-suite-2026) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 14 Tf 0.050 0.250 0.450 rg 54.00 197.25 Td (B6. How to start FPGA AI Suite each time on Linux) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 171.75 Td (Open a terminal and start the existing container:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 149.25 Td (docker start -ai fpga-ai-suite-2026) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 128.62 Td (You are inside FPGA AI Suite when the prompt changes from the host prompt, for example:) Tj ET
BT /Courier 8.5 Tf 0.050 0.050 0.050 rg 66.00 106.12 Td (sahilpat@sahilpat:~$) Tj ET
BT /Helvetica 10 Tf 0.000 0.000 0.000 rg 54.00 85.50 Td (to the container prompt, for example:) Tj ET
